Bootstrap Integration: Bootstrap is included via CDN for both CSS and JS.
Header Section: The header features a background image, a large title, a subtitle, and a call-to-action button.
Features Section: This section uses Bootstrap's grid system to create a three-column layout, each featuring an icon, title, and description.
Call to Action Section: A background image with a prominent call to action.
Contact Section: A simple contact form with fields for name, email, and message.
Footer Section: A simple footer with copyright information.
This setup ensures a responsive design that adjusts well to different screen sizes thanks to Bootstrap's grid system and responsive classes. The custom CSS is used to add additional styling like background images, fonts, and spacing.
